589
01:08:51,436 --> 01:08:54,537
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku ingin kau selalu merasa bahagia, Yeon Hui.</i></font>

590
01:08:54,537 --> 01:08:55,537
<font color="yellow"><i>Oraboni!</i></font>

591
01:08:56,436 --> 01:09:00,136
<font color="yellow"><i>Jika kita tidak menghilangkan kutukannya
